The paper deals with fairness in automated decision-making systems, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of data streams, which suggests that cs.CY (Computers and Society) may be relevant. Additionally, the paper proposes interventions to modify input data, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
